    &lt;Title&gt;Scan and bloods&lt;/Title&gt;
    &lt;ScreenName&gt;Philip&lt;/ScreenName&gt;
    &lt;CommentText&gt;What an excellent team of professionals at Chorley hospital. 
This afternoon I was sent by my GP to Chorley for a blood test and ultrasound scan. Unfortunately the blood test department had just closed, but the nurse in charge said no problem, I will stay open for you. What a nice lady. 
Next was my scan. The two nurses had me in 15 minutes before my appointment. How often has that ever happened to you? The two extremely pleasant ladies examined me and did the business without a problem. 
Plus let's not forget the receptionists who were a pleasure to deal with.
Well done Chorley Hospital you are a shining example of how the NHS should be. Thank you all. We do appreciate all your efforts.


&lt;/CommentText&gt;
